{"tid":12813,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"這豬肉好猥褻 地方媽媽誤認是男人陰莖","createTime":"2016-11-29T21:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T22:25:02.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f62faea6b475f32f51876f38f3b9205c03ee9822","tid":12813,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T21:44:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160109/640_55a9e46fbb322002cb2b9a84adca4623.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160109%2F640_55a9e46fbb322002cb2b9a84adca4623.jpg&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=4c494ce3\" target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160109/640_55a9e46fbb322002cb2b9a84adca4623.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n英國一名36歲地方媽媽瓦特(Louise Watt)日前上超市買菜，開心地買了一盒豬腰肉，但回到家後仔細一看，發現這和豬肉好「猥褻」，害她以為看到男人巨型陽具。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《都市報》報導，瓦特解釋說：「買菜的時候我一邊顧著6歲和2歲的孩子，我拿起豬肉時只顧看肉質顏色和日期，完全沒有在意它的『形狀』。」瓦特之後利用這盒豬肉為家人們做晚餐，不過與平常不一樣的是，做晚餐的期間她拿著相機一直拍，就是要拍下這「猥褻豬肉」的進化史。<br />\n<br />\n她隨後也把照片上傳網路，引發網友討論和迴響，就有網友問她：「你很『滿足』嗎？」、「想要來點新鮮的嗎？」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"195d0e697d702c034a621c8a94560d9aed2cdffd","tid":12813,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T21:51:16.000Z","msg":"施旖婕連豬肉都撈埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd8f422b34422ade2aed040f848582e47fcc60f","tid":12813,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T21:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>施旖婕連豬肉都撈埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a382a47d1f80124848809ccbcc15daa4c502fa3","tid":12813,"uid":1351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T21:52:14.000Z","msg":"巴打仲係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d1b3